2022 might be the first year that the majority of us get to visit movie theaters year-round since this pandemic started, and boy do we have some things to get excited for. Join us as we discuss what 2022 has in store for us comic book fans as we go over every feature film (based on a comic book character) set to be released this year! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

